data.description: Step into the home of your dreams! Like new, this D.R. Horton, Hayden Plan has 5BR/3BA home with a loft and is move in ready. Formal dining room greets you as you enter the home. Beautiful kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, walk in pantry, extra-large island that sits 3-4 bar stools with a touchless faucet & double sink on the opposite side of island. Eat in kitchen area that overlooks family/great room with a lovely wood trim accent wall & a fireplace. Updated lights & laminate vinyl hardwood floors on the main level. Guest bedroom & full bath on the main level that can also be used as an office. Upstairs features an oversized master suite with a sitting area. Master bath has double vanities, large soaking tub, separate glass shower and a private water closet. Enjoy using your walk-in customized closet. The loft is a bonus to this home, offering extra space to gather for game or movie nights with friends and family. Three additional generously sized bedrooms with a full bath, dual vanities & shower tub combo. Custom walk-in laundry room with built in cabinets. Step outside and enjoy morning coffee or evening cocktails as you hang out in the privacy of your fenced back yard with its extended patio to accommodate several of your grills & lawn furniture. Don't let the opportunity slip away to make this property your own. Schedule a private tour today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you in the picture-perfect haven!
